 <h3>Platform security layers</h3>
 <p>We at Ai Mr Ferdy Pro protect your account and funds through industry-standard encryption and verification. All data transmitted between your device and our servers uses SSL encryption — a technology that scrambles your information so it cannot be intercepted. During account creation, we collect your identity and address information through our KYC (Know Your Customer) verification process. This step typically takes subject to verification and confirms your eligibility to use the platform. We store all personal data in secure, encrypted databases. Two-factor authentication is available for added security — enable it in your account settings to require a second verification step during login. Your password should be unique and complex; never share it with anyone. If you suspect unauthorized access, reset your password immediately and contact our English support team. All transactions — deposits, withdrawals, and game activity — are logged and encrypted. You can review your complete transaction history anytime from your account dashboard.</p>

 <h3>Game fairness and RTP</h3>
 <p>We at Ai Mr Ferdy Pro operate two distinct game categories, each with different fairness mechanisms. Live-dealer tables are broadcast in real time from professional HD studios. Professional dealers conduct all games — Baccarat, Roulette, Blackjack, Dragon Tiger, Sic Bo, Andar Bahar, Teen Patti — according to established rules. You watch the game unfold on camera; the outcome depends on physical cards, spin wheels, or dice, not software. Slot games and other automated titles use a Random Number Generator (RNG), a certified algorithm that ensures every spin outcome is unpredictable and independent. RNG-based games carry an RTP (Return to Player) percentage — a statistical measure indicating the average payout over a very large number of plays. For example, a slot with returns an average of 96 units per 100 units wagered over millions of spins. RTP is not a guaranteed personal outcome; individual sessions vary widely. All our slot providers — PG Soft, Quickspin, Yggdrasil, Big Time Gaming — use certified RNG systems audited by independent laboratories. Live-dealer games have no RTP percentage; outcomes depend on dealer actions and physical events.</p>

